Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteReasons

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteReasons
public class JDBWasteReasons extends Object
The JDBWasteReasons class updates the table APP_WASTE_REASONS. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Transaction Type as stored in the APP_WASTE_REASONS table.
